@USClaireForce @Grady_Booch @synoptase I am suggesting that generative art should be subject to copyright law in *exactly* the same way as human-produced art.
Copying is copyright infringement, regardless of the production process.
Learning from others in order to create new artifacts isn't.

@armchair_prof I do admit when I'm wrong.
I would be a pretty terrible scientists if I wasn't capable of that.
